":"461d234713f95ed294dfb903f3e417164693d608","tid":1053970,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45ff2128813bc6d61dd8745df6fb334455d450c0","tid":1053970,"uid":52056,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6793f2b5b15dcdaf6a178fe3a589e73f78c195cd","tid":1053970,"uid":127791,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T21:55:00.000Z","msg":"最尾打鬥好正 由另一隊個隊長一個一個咁介紹掃毒組啲隊員 原來個個都咁把炮咁好打 但平時就咁弱智 呢個反差好那正<br />\n尤其係佢哋本身Team人都睇唔起掃毒組"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"局長同隊長講要解散team人嗰時，隊長提到緝毒隊係局長親自揀人<br />\n原來係伏筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"你覺唔覺局長成個文在寅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"冇留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f43814b3c4e49fe2fea6ae1212fe45514bf4d85","tid":1053970,"uid":132524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇左<br />\n9.5/10 笑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9913027edea7345874fbdc11725536dfce65be1","tid":1053970,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:29:18.000Z","msg":"中間訓著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時係幾好笑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8651ee57fa08d904ae605a3c89e4e758dc383c4f","tid":1053970,"uid":14225,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"好搞笑，估唔到呢套韓國電影，<br />\n居然充滿着80，90年代港產片嘅元素。<br />\n<br />\n仲用上張國榮既 《當年情》做插曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又到咗4月1日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8438e39174ea8c4a37aaf44ae2de1e765d6a656b","tid":1053970,"uid":35249,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />套嘢最後播當年情致敬<br />\n可想言之韓仔有幾中意當年嘅香港<br />\n香港文化又有幾大影響力<br />\n<br />\n播個陣我男朋友問係咪搞錯咗<br />\n我話韓仔好中意張國榮㗎～"},{"pid":"89a29531748116d88d4ea7df945d176dbb053478","tid":1053970,"uid":136952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ebb12aca5291582a92df853ccdb900053f896cad","tid":1053970,"uid":234462,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"當韓國仲珍惜同尊重港產片，香港d偽港產片日日要刷大陸人鞋，我覺得人呢套真係俾足面喎，成套戲有種80,90年代港產喜劇影子同節奏，我覺得好好笑，第一條橋係幾有趣，簡單易明，第二佢好大膽放棄了好多韓國電影的感情或扭橋位 ，(就算車太絃 的開心鬼上身或最出名的我的野蠻女友都係要扭一扭，等你感動) 呢套戲叫盡量做返以前港產片中五分鐘一小笑，十分鐘一大笑。佢好直接就係為了娛樂同輕鬆的。<br />\n<br />\n我都係睇80.90港產片大，我覺得香港人愈來愈唔知想要乜，周星星已經過了那段時間，留低只有舊片，我們繼續用以前做準則，想有咁的喜劇已經好難。有時候寧願睇韓片，美片甚至法國喜劇反而仲揾到那種天馬行空喜劇的感覺。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"香港人真係愈黎愈難服侍<br />\n入場睇戲但求合家歡<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆兩鐘<br />\n幾分鐘就一個笑位<br />\n今時今日 已經好難得"},{"pid":"f1c55d2e0924990c5a97c6761cb8fa78247eb92f","tid":1053970,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"入場前淨係望左梁柏堅講幾句話會有驚喜<br />\n但估唔到成套戲出黎好似90年代港產喜劇"},{"pid":"838bb7333c73a0aca8fd5388d560d1fe92e21f30","tid":1053970,"uid":171990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"冇期望下睇左 idea ok 但笑料唔岩口味 可能韓仔buy<br />\n<br />\n如果提港產原素 實在要推薦呢套<br />\n到宜家我都覺得好高質 當年的演員真係好高汁<br />\nGun and Talks (2000)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/85/Guns_%26_Talks_poster.jpg/220px-Guns_%26_Talks_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F8%2F85%2FGuns_%2526_Talks_poster.jpg%2F220px-Guns_%2526_Talks_poster.jpg&h=bd408313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一位係炸雞做奸角 不過瘦左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe2a300285cd41217261044e6c69cdb14543e76","tid":1053970,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e222789efd39a60fbf75ce66eae7544e14cba9","tid":1053970,"uid":6152,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6793f2b5b15dcdaf6a178fe3a589e73f78c195cd","tid":1053970,"uid":127791,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"199ad8d5696f65735aee16ea8246d6859d774810","tid":1053970,"uid":1408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:39:53.000Z","msg":"嫌打鬥少少長<br />\n其他都幾好 輕輕鬆鬆又2個鐘"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T21:55:00.000Z","msg":"最尾打鬥好正 由另一隊個隊長一個一個咁介紹掃毒組啲隊員 原來個個都咁把炮咁好打 但平時就咁弱智 呢個反差好那正<br />\n尤其係佢哋本身Team人都睇唔起掃毒組"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"同意 幾好睇<br />\n我個人認為打鬥係最尾1on1 耐左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"反而幾鐘意最尾各成員場1on1打鬥<br />\n開頭有d無聊以為吹大左，點知去到開炸雞鋪後黎料<br />\n好有娛樂性，做笑位手法幾乎係全盛港產笑片咁<br />\n諗起而家d港產商業片柒下柒下咁真係無眼睇"},{"pid":"3794f72426be532704fc1e607a99fcac32603209","tid":1053970,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94099805d2a956f1f693bf9a1d569cd8cd83eacc","tid":1053970,"uid":3656,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzqNsJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzqNsJW.png&h=91796323&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"本身最尾呢幕幾好笑，起歌一刻又撞正今日有d感慨<br />\n<br />\n有觀眾嘩左聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d5de740b29bc5036d2a1f60ea7cf31e3235488","tid":1053970,"uid":6436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3794f72426be532704fc1e607a99fcac32603209","tid":1053970,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94099805d2a956f1f693bf9a1d569cd8cd83eacc","tid":